{"tid":2085208,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"路爾斯減薪助阿仙奴增兵","createTime":"2020-06-29T17:49:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T18:43:17.000Z","uid":72497,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"72f3cac7c588741d3129e7e8852cc8043dd0906c","tid":2085208,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T17:49:05.000Z","msg":"大衛路爾斯早前續約阿仙奴，引來廠迷鬧爆，但原來這名巴西國腳為了球會的將來，願意減人工。<br />\n<br />\n大衛路爾斯（David Luiz）在去年夏天以800萬鎊從車路士加盟阿仙奴，簽約1年，周薪12.5萬鎊，原本是球隊第5高人工的球員。 不過，根據英國《電訊報》報道，路爾斯早前跟兵工廠續約1年時接受了減薪，好讓球隊有財政空間去買斷中堅柏保路馬里、右閘蘇亞利斯。 總監伊度就曾表示：「我很高興球隊未來有這些球員在陣，他們一直是領隊阿迪達跟我的計劃之中，為球隊帶來正確的平衡。」 <br />\n<br />\n不少廠迷早前得知路爾斯就算在場上犯錯頻頻，仍然獲得續約，紗紗在網上狂鬧阿仙奴。未知他們得知路爾斯的苦心後，會不會改變想法？"},{"pid":"772ee7b43858138b91988a0b254a01851d42f009","tid":2085208,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T17:49:28.000Z","msg":"唔反了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5067c3179c51e8bc601bd0c4d97584209e44bc8a","tid":2085208,"uid":151324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T17:51:08.000Z","msg":"又要上前6 又要踢歐霸<br />\n呢個價真係得佢最好"},{"pid":"351293c44632efeba083e9126b68697e666e641e","tid":2085208,"uid":30070,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T17:51:43.000Z","msg":"走左咪仲多筆直<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a084177383123d44d0c8b61efe9590bf00f30f58","tid":2085208,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T18:22:03.000Z","msg":"真阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88ca1257d28f88327b4cda44e7036c76ae503317","tid":2085208,"uid":72497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"351293c44632efeba083e9126b68697e666e641e","tid":2085208,"uid":30070,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T17:51:43.000Z","msg":"走左